1. *Šefa* je odlučila da svi zaposleni dobiju povećanje plata. (The boss decided that all employees should get a pay raise.)

2. Ona ne postuje *šefu* i nije zadovoljna s njegovim rešenjem. (She doesn't respect the boss and is not satisfied with his decision.)

3. Ona je postala *šefa* kompanije pre tri godine. (She became the head of the company three years ago.)

4. Nastavnik je postao *šef* radne grupe koja proizvodi računare. (The teacher became the head of the working group producing computers.)

5. *Šefov* stav je da treba da se radno vreme produži. (The boss's stance is that working hours should be extended.)

6. *Šefu* je potrebna pomoć za rešavanje problema. (The boss needs help to solve the problem.)